column5:
I know, I have a very supportive family. We have no money problems, no drama, everyone is healthy and gets along well. 
And yet I feel like med school is draining my energy. Everyone around me seems so motivated. I barely managed to pass the exams, I know it’s because I don’t work as hard as some people yet I complain about my bad grades like a spoiled child.
I just want a break.
